The Fremennik blade is a Fremennik weapon equivalent to an adamant scimitar. It is dropped by Fremennik warriors, and various monsters on Waterbirth Island. Completion of The Fremennik Trials and 30 Attack is required to equip the weapon. Although the sword is not tradeable, it is possible to cast alchemy spells on the blade.

Bardur, located in the Waterbirth Island dungeon, will trade you cooked Sharks for Fremennik blades, Fremennik shields or Fremennik helms.
